by Nek- at 2017-06-19T05:16:28Z

Hello,

Thanks for your contribution!

Please fix your code using the fabbot fix:
```
$ curl http://fabbot.io/patch/symfony/symfony/23222/f6a94cb56fc544f66e39e0658143976c852a14bb/cs.diff | patch -p0
```
Then [squash](http://gitready.com/advanced/2009/02/10/squashing-commits-with-rebase.html) your commits so there is still only one commit.

